"Prende un layer poligonale o lineare e ne genera uno nuovo in cui le "
"geometrie hanno un numero di vertici maggiore di quello originale."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1909
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1999
msgid ""
"If the geometries have Z or M values present then these will be linearly "
"interpolated at the added vertices."
msgstr ""
"Se le geometrie hanno valori Z o M presenti, questi saranno interpolati "
"linearmente ai vertici aggiunti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1912
msgid ""
"The number of new vertices to add to each segment is specified as an input "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"Il numero di nuovi vertici da aggiungere ad ogni segmento è specificato come"
" parametro in ingresso."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1918
msgid "Red points show the vertices before and after the densify"
msgstr "I punti rossi mostrano i vertici prima e dopo l'addensamento"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1926
msgid ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1944
msgid "**Vertices to add**"
msgstr "**Vertici da aggiungere**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1945
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2814
msgid "``VERTICES``"
msgstr "``VERTICES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1948
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2266
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3310
