msgstr "Rimuove i valori Z dalle geometrie"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2365
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2388
msgid "**Z/M Dropped**"
msgstr "**Z/M Dropped**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2391
msgid ""
"The output vector layer (identical to the input layer, except that the M "
"and/or Z dimensions have been removed from the geometries)."
msgstr ""
"Il layer vettoriale in uscita (identico al layer in ingresso, tranne per il "
"fatto che le dimensioni M e/o Z sono state rimosse dalle geometrie)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2398
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:dropmzvalues``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``native:dropmzvalues``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2408
msgid "Eliminate selected polygons"
msgstr "Elimina i poligoni selezionati"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2409
msgid ""
"Combines selected polygons of the input layer with certain adjacent polygons"
" by erasing their common boundary. The adjacent polygon can be either the "
"one with the largest or smallest area or the one sharing the largest common "
"boundary with the polygon to be eliminated."
msgstr ""
"Combina i poligoni selezionati del layer in ingresso con alcuni poligoni "
"adiacenti cancellando il loro confine comune. Il poligono adiacente può "
"essere quello con l'area più grande o più piccola o quello che condivide il "
"confine comune più grande con il poligono da eliminare."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2415
msgid ""
"Eliminate is normally used to get rid of sliver polygons, i.e. tiny polygons"
" that are a result of polygon intersection processes where boundaries of the"
" inputs are similar but not identical."
msgstr ""
"Elimina i poligoni selezionati è normalmente usato per sbarazzarsi dei "
"poligoni sliver, cioè dei piccoli poligoni che sono il risultato di processi"
" di intersezione di poligoni dove i confini degli elementi in ingresso sono "
"simili ma non identici."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2421
msgid ":ref:`qgisfixgeometries`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisfixgeometries`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2439
msgid "**Merge selection with the neighboring polygon with the**"
msgstr "**Fusione della selezione al poligono più vicino**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2440
msgid "``MODE``"
msgstr "``MODE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2443
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3121
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3129
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3224
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3232
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5717
msgid "Default: Not set"
msgstr "Valore predefinito: non impostato"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2444
msgid ""
"Choose the parameter to use in order to get rid of the selected polygons:"
msgstr ""
"Scegli il parametro da utilizzare per ottenere eliminazioni tra i poligoni "
"selezionati:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2447
msgid "0 --- Largest Area"
msgstr "0 --- Area più grande"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2448
msgid "1 --- Smallest Area"
msgstr "1 --- Area più piccola"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2449
msgid "2 --- Largest Common Boundary"
msgstr "2 --- Confine comune più grande "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2451
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2474
msgid "**Eliminated**"
msgstr "**Eliminati**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2477
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3920
msgid "The output polygon vector layer."
msgstr "Il layer vettoriale poligonale in uscita."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2482
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2492
msgid "Explode lines"
msgstr "Esplodi linee"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2493
msgid ""
"Takes a lines layer and creates a new one in which each line layer is "
"replaced by a set of lines representing the segments in the original line."
msgstr ""
"Prende un layer lineare e ne crea uno nuovo in cui ogni layer lineare è "
"sostituito da un insieme di linee che rappresentano i segmenti della linea "
"originale."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2497
msgid ""
